[2] Wisconsin (Vernon county)
Date: Fri 9 Nov 2018 03:59 PM CST
Source: News8000 [edited]
https://www.news8000.com/news/vernon-county-confirms- multiple-cases-of-whooping-cough/854036971


Viroqua [Vernon county] Area Schools released a statement today [9 Nov 2018] notifying parents of confirmed cases of whooping cough (pertussis) in Vernon county. According to the release, a couple of teens in the community are being treated for the illness.

The statement shared information on recognizing the symptoms and the steps to take to confirm and care for the person who's ill.

[Byline: Deb Brazil]

